OL,5, Facial recognition was used on crowds  
OL,6, attending a Beyonce concert in Cardiff 
OL,7, to scan for paedophiles and terrorists.
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police and Crime           
OL,10,FCommissioner Alun Michael said         
OL,11,Fsearching for potential terrorists at  
OL,12,Fsuch events had become normal since the
OL,13,F2017 Manchester Arena bombing.         
OL,15,FHe said paedophiles were also targeted 
OL,16,Fas "there would be very large numbers  
OL,17,Fof young girls attending that concert".
OL,19,FMr Michael described using such cameras
